overview: These are the stories of babysitters; their title might explain their job but really, there's more than meets the eye with each of these babes. Sneaky, and only after one thing ? hung cock from their proprietors! Cassidy decides to go sneaking around Jordan's house and ends up catching him naked in the shower. She gets so turned on that she can't help but watch - that is until Jordan catches her red handed. Natasha is desperate for a babysitting gig, so Manuel hires her for some help. When he comes home to find her resting on the couch, she knows there is only one way to make it up to him. Whitney is hired to help Mr. Pete out around the house, including taking care of him when he isn't feeling well. She knows exactly what kind of medicine he needs to get back in shape. Devious Piper decides to sneak her boyfriend into the house she is babysitting in for a little fun. They need to be careful though, too much noise might make them get caught!
title: Babysitter Diaries 16
